📄 Privacy Policy – Vibe Player

Vibe Player is a free and open-source multimedia player app. This SERVICE is provided by us at no cost and is intended for use as is.

This page informs users regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decides to use our Service.

By using Vibe Player, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

📊 Information Collection and Use

For a better experience, while using our Service, we may require you to provide certain personally identifiable information. However:

👉 We do not directly collect or store personal data on our servers.
👉 Any data remains on your device unless shared with third-party services.

🔗 Third-Party Services

Vibe Player uses trusted third-party services that may collect information to improve functionality and performance:

Google Play Services
Google Analytics for Firebase
Firebase Crashlytics

These services may collect anonymized data such as device information, usage statistics, and crash logs.

📱 App Usage Data

To improve user experience, Vibe Player may access:

List of installed apps (used for compatibility and feature suggestions)
Device information (OS version, device type)

This data is used only for:

Improving app performance
Enhancing compatibility
Providing better user experience
📄 Log Data

In case of errors, we may collect Log Data through third-party tools. This may include:

Device IP address
Device name
Operating system version
App configuration
Time and date of usage

This data is used strictly for debugging and improving the app.

🍪 Cookies

Vibe Player does not use cookies directly. However, third-party services may use cookies or similar technologies to collect information.

You can choose to accept or refuse cookies through your device settings.

